In this unit, you'll find the tools and support you need to implement Khan Academy biology in your classroom. With our unit guides, you'll discover lesson objectives, detailed teaching tips, common misconceptions, NGSS standards alignments, and example phenomena to motivate student learning. With our hands-on activities, you'll make science come alive in your classroom. With our creativity and biology professional series, you'll inspire students to follow a path in STEM. Get ready to transform your classroom into a hub of exploration and discovery!

In this unit, we’ll get into the mechanisms of evolution. We’ll explore how natural selection, adaptation, speciation, and group behavior shape the living world around us. This journey will provide a deeper understanding of the complex processes that drive the diversity and survival of species on our planet.

**Unit guides are here!** Power up your classroom with engaging strategies, tools, and activities from Khan Academy’s learning experts. [**Doc**](https://bit.ly/3FPP9Xa) | [**PDF**](https://bit.ly/3Y7ylRC)

In this unit, we'll go from micro to macro as we explore the cellular basis of life. We’ll discover the intricate worlds of prokaryotic and eukaryotic cells, delve into the organization of multicellular life, and examine human body systems. We’ll also learn how organisms masterfully maintain balance through homeostasis.

**Unit guides are here!** Power up your classroom with engaging strategies, tools, and activities from Khan Academy’s learning experts. [**Doc**](https://bit.ly/42k50oy) | [**PDF**](https://bit.ly/4jc0nDJ)

In this unit, we’ll explore the dynamic processes that drive cellular and developmental biology. We’ll investigate mitosis to understand cell division, then examine how the cell cycle is regulated and how disruptions can lead to cancer. We’ll journey through the stages of fertilization, cell differentiation, and development, witnessing the remarkable transformation from a single cell to a complex organism.

**Unit guides are here!** Power up your classroom with engaging strategies, tools, and activities from Khan Academy’s learning experts. [**Doc**](https://bit.ly/4i0r3X5) | [**PDF**](https://bit.ly/3FR3ZN1)
